{
  "text": "DNA from the isolates was prepared and the presence of tandem repeats in the cyp51A promoter region was detected by a simple PCR assay described recently. [CITATION_1] Other triazole resistance-conferring mutations within the structural gene were detected by PCR amplification followed by direct DNA sequencing of cyp51A, as described in detail previously. [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] The study was approved by the Ethics Committee, Faculty of Medicine, Kuwait University.",
